WEBVTT

00:03.368 --> 00:05.737
¶ Boy, the way
Glenn Miller played ¶

00:05.805 --> 00:09.273
¶ songs that made
the hit parade ¶

00:09.341 --> 00:12.943
¶ guys like us
we had it made ¶

00:13.012 --> 00:16.247
[ together ]
¶ those were the days ¶

00:16.315 --> 00:19.484
<i>¶ and you knew</i>
<i> </i> <i> where you were then ¶</i>

00:19.551 --> 00:23.054
[ Archie ]
¶ girls were girls
and men were men ¶

00:23.122 --> 00:26.024
[ Archie, Edith ]
¶ mister, we could use a man ¶

00:26.092 --> 00:29.828
¶ like Herbert hoover again ¶

00:29.895 --> 00:33.231
[ Archie ]
¶ didn't need no welfare state ¶

00:33.298 --> 00:36.735
[ Edith ]
¶ everybody pulled his weight ¶

00:36.802 --> 00:40.438
[ Archie, Edith ]
¶ gee, our old lasalle
ran great ¶

00:40.506 --> 00:46.177
¶ those were the days ¶

00:53.185 --> 00:55.120
¶ [ humming ]

01:02.962 --> 01:05.196
<i>[ Doorbell ringing ]</i>
<i>Coming!</i>

01:10.235 --> 01:13.004
Oh!
Is Michael stivic here?

01:13.072 --> 01:15.707
I'm afraid not.
Can I help you?

01:15.775 --> 01:18.543
Well, you see,
I've had something of his
for four years,

01:18.610 --> 01:20.745
and now I'd like
for him to have it.

01:20.813 --> 01:22.747
Oh.

01:24.183 --> 01:26.685
That's very nice of you.
What is it?

01:26.752 --> 01:29.821
His son.

01:29.889 --> 01:32.791
Son?
Oh, no!

01:32.858 --> 01:35.126
No, miss--
I mean, come back!

01:35.194 --> 01:37.962
I don't think--
please!

01:38.030 --> 01:41.700
Missus--
oh, my!

01:41.767 --> 01:45.970
She's made
a terrible mistake,
little boy.

01:46.038 --> 01:48.106
Was that lady your mommy?

01:49.842 --> 01:51.776
And Mike--

01:51.844 --> 01:55.780
oh, my.
What are we gonna do?

01:55.848 --> 01:59.450
You see,
Gloria is upstairs.

01:59.518 --> 02:02.320
Well, here,
take off your coat.

02:02.387 --> 02:05.356
I'm sure your mommy
will be right back...

02:05.424 --> 02:08.292
As soon as she finds out
it's the wrong house.

02:08.360 --> 02:10.294
What's your name?

02:11.731 --> 02:14.099
Is it Billy?

02:14.166 --> 02:17.435
Jimmy? Tommy?

02:17.502 --> 02:19.804
Will you tell me
if I guess it?

02:22.141 --> 02:24.375
Oh, dear.
[ Gloria ]
Ma, are you talking to Michael?

02:24.443 --> 02:26.677
Uh, just a minute,
Gloria.

02:26.746 --> 02:28.913
You see, that's Gloria.

02:28.981 --> 02:32.050
Now, don't let on
why you're here.

02:34.186 --> 02:37.088
Uh, it-it ain't Michael,
Gloria.

02:37.156 --> 02:39.624
Your name ain't Michael,
is it?
[ Footfalls descending stairs ]

02:39.691 --> 02:43.862
Hey, ma,
what a cute little boy.
Where did he come from?

02:43.929 --> 02:47.165
I don't know.

02:47.233 --> 02:50.668
I-I mean, I do know.
Oh, he came through
the front door.

02:50.736 --> 02:53.304
That's where
he came from.
Huh?

02:53.372 --> 02:55.606
Will you help me
fix the dinner, Gloria?

02:55.674 --> 02:58.576
No. I wanna know
who the little boy is.

02:58.644 --> 03:02.413
Hi there, big fella.
Who are you? Hey, ma,
who does he belong to?

03:02.481 --> 03:05.316
Oh, um--

03:05.384 --> 03:08.452
some lady.
I don't think you know her.

03:08.520 --> 03:10.321
Oh, don't tell me
you're baby-sitting?

03:10.389 --> 03:13.324
Yeah, yeah.
Something like that.
<i>Oh.</i>

03:13.392 --> 03:16.394
Hi there, big fella.
What's your name?

03:16.461 --> 03:18.930
Oh, ma, look at that.

03:18.998 --> 03:21.966
Isn't that cute? When he pouts
he looks just like Michael.

03:22.034 --> 03:24.936
No! No--
oh.

03:25.004 --> 03:30.008
I mean,
Mike has a mustache.
Yeah.

03:30.075 --> 03:32.443
I'll bet he's hungry.

03:32.511 --> 03:35.713
You are hungry,
aren't you?

03:35.781 --> 03:38.349
You see, Gloria?
He's starved.

03:38.417 --> 03:40.384
Come on, dear.
Sit over here,

03:40.452 --> 03:42.753
and Gloria will go
out in the kitchen
and make you...

03:42.822 --> 03:45.290
A nice peanut butter
and jelly sandwich.

03:45.357 --> 03:47.625
But, ma, he just said
he wasn't hungry.

03:47.693 --> 03:49.727
Little boys
are always hungry.

03:49.795 --> 03:53.464
Please, make a peanut butter
and jelly sandwich.

03:53.532 --> 03:58.102
Little boy, if we bring you
a nice peanut butter
and jelly sandwich,

03:58.170 --> 04:00.104
would you tell me
your name?

04:00.172 --> 04:02.707
But you've got to.

04:04.343 --> 04:08.479
Where do you live?
What's your mommy's name?

04:08.547 --> 04:11.015
- Hi, Gloria, I'm home.
- Hi, Mike.

04:11.083 --> 04:14.252
Hi, ma.
Gloria's in the kitchen.

04:14.320 --> 04:16.254
Oh, thanks.

